## **Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)**

**How far in advance should I book my wedding transportation?**

It’s recommended to book at least 3-6 months in advance, especially during peak wedding seasons.

**Do drivers assist with luggage or personal items?**

Yes, our professional drivers are happy to assist with loading and unloading personal items to ensure a hassle-free experience.

**Is there an option for additional stops?**

Absolutely! We can accommodate additional stops within Miami and surrounding areas. Please discuss your itinerary with us in advance.

**How is pricing structured: hourly or flat rate?**

We offer both hourly rates and flat fees depending on your needs. Contact us for a customized quote that suits your schedule and route.

